commentary: Hasan Ali to H Masakadza, OUT sends two stumps flying away! Squares Masakadza up. Length ball on off, and the ball angles slightly away after pitching. Masakadza tries to drive straight, but the ball goes past his outside edge, and uproots off- and middle-stump. A funny celebration too - Hasan chooses not to do the blast celebration, and instead asks his friend Shadab to celebrate for him. Remember, Hasan pulled a neck muscle the last time he tried to do that.
shortText: Hasan Ali to H Masakadza, OUT
text: sends two stumps flying away! Squares Masakadza up. Length ball on off, and the ball angles slightly away after pitching. Masakadza tries to drive straight, but the ball goes past his outside edge, and uproots off- and middle-stump. A funny celebration too - Hasan chooses not to do the blast celebration, and instead asks his friend Shadab to celebrate for him. Remember, Hasan pulled a neck muscle the last time he tried to do that.
